> Cynthia Villalba, Universidad Nacional de Asunci=C3=B3n, Paraguay
>
> SLISW provides a forum for the Latin American community of Software
> Engineering to
> exchange ideas, experiences and research results among teachers,
> researchers, industry
> professionals and students.
>
> Original contributions are sought in the broad framework of Software
> Engineering,
> comprising academic research, industrial and business applications that
> both make an impact
> and provide lessons on their development.
>
>
>
> *SLIOIA - Latin American Symposium on Operations Research and Artificial
