>
> SLIOIA provides a forum for the Latin American community of Artificial
> Intelligence and
> Operations Research to exchange ideas, experiences and research results
> among teachers,
> researchers, students and industry professionals. Original contributions
> are sought in
> the diverse areas of Artificial Intelligence and Operations Research,
> comprising academic
> research, industrial and business applications that both make an impact
> and provide
> lessons on their development.
>
