> *SLTC - Latin American Symposium on Theory of Computation *Chairs:
> Jes=C3=BAs Aranda Bueno, Universidad del Valle, Colombia
> Pablo Castro, Universidad Nacional de R=C3=ADo Cuarto, Argentina
>
> SLTC is an event that brings together the Latin American community of
> Theory of Computation
> in aforum to exchange ideas, experiences and research results among
> teachers, researchers,
> and students. This symposium focuses on the advances in the disciplines o=
f
> Theory of Algorithms,
> Computability and Complexity, Automata and Formal Languages, Principles
