> Gabriela Mar=C3=ADn, Universidad de Costa Rica, Costa Rica
> Jos=C3=A9 Francisco Tirado Fern=C3=A1ndez, Universidad Complutense de Mad=
rid, Espa=C3=B1a
>
> CLTD aims at disseminating the work of Latin American students who have
> recently completed
