> Eric Gamess - Jacksonville State University, USA
> Daniel Guidoni -Universidade Federal de S=C3=A3o Jo=C3=A3o del Rei, Brazi=
l
>
> LANC is an international technical forum for experts from industry and
> academia from around the world,
> but especially from Latin American countries, to exchange ideas and
